snippet.title: Bracket Chain (Early Gameplay Demo) - TRAILER
snippet.description:
Follow the robot Bracket as he ventures out of his technology-driven home realm and into a mysterious new realm governed exclusively by magic in this action-packed indie adventure!

Bracket Chain: Early Gameplay Demo is coming to a download link near you on December 8th! Don't miss it!

LINKS:

SOCIAL MEDIA UPDATES - https://x.com/alumae_star
